00:38:11,555 --> 00:38:15,222
(peaceful electronic music)

517
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:32,763
(knocks)

518
00:38:42,890 --> 00:38:43,910
- [Billy] Oh.

519
00:38:43,910 --> 00:38:45,113
Hi. (chuckles)
- Billy.

520
00:38:46,120 --> 00:38:48,578
You got any cigarettes?
- Well, sure.

521
00:38:48,578 --> 00:38:49,411
Sure.

522
00:38:50,944 --> 00:38:52,313
Here you go.
- Thanks.

523
00:38:53,310 --> 00:38:54,590
We're still waiting for our money.

524
00:38:54,590 --> 00:38:55,730
- Well, I haven't gotten paid yet.

525
00:38:55,730 --> 00:38:57,060
- Well, somebody got paid.

526
00:38:57,060 --> 00:38:59,850
Me and Tom are on your
local news stands nude.

