to see any of this, okay?

752
00:53:12,850 --> 00:53:14,030
Go on, hey, get away from there.

753
00:53:14,030 --> 00:53:15,250
Go on, Jane.

754
00:53:15,250 --> 00:53:17,393
Jane, just drive off, just go home, go on.

755
00:53:29,635 --> 00:53:34,635
(horn honks)
(tires screech)

756
00:53:45,740 --> 00:53:46,740
- You alright, lady?

757
00:53:50,530 --> 00:53:51,753
- I wanna go home!

758
00:53:52,740 --> 00:53:53,573
- Where's home?

759
00:53:55,110 --> 00:53:56,010
- Plymouth Street!

760
00:53:57,740 --> 00:53:58,573
- That's easy.

761
00:53:59,600 --> 00:54:00,953
That's highland over there.

762
00:54:02,033 --> 00:54:04,443
Take a right, you go straight down.

763
00:54:05,840 --> 00:54:06,880
- Right, thanks.

764
00:54:10,508 --> 00:54:11,341
- Hey, lady!

765
00:54:11,341 --> 00:54:12,697
Do you want me to go with you?

766
00:54:15,619 --> 00:54:18,036
(Jane sighs)

